  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this pilot project is to see if a supplemental form of dietary gangliosides
      can serve as a potential treatment for the rare metabolic condition called ganglioside GM3
      synthase deficiency.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
